{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_52_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 呪われてしまったんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺は呪われてしまうのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Am I being cursed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんの顔色が真っ青に……\nどうしよう、呪いや祟りのことを強く言い過ぎたかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}'s face is pale…\nWhat should I do? Maybe I have exaggerated the curse and suffer",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　おみくじを引いて運試ししませんか？\nここの神社のおみくじは少し変わってるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right! Why don't we try our luck by drawing a fortune slip?\nThe fortune slip at this shrine are a little unusual",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.3000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おみくじか……。それでいい結果が出れば\n少しは安心出来るかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fortune slip… If I get a good result‚\nI might feel a little more be relieved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7533.3335877,
          "startTime": 32.566666921
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ！\n行きましょう、おみくじはこっちです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right!\nGo ahead‚ fortune slips are this way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.033330663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "このおみくじの紙を水で濡らすのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shall I soaking this fortune slip paper in water?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1333268484,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、そうすると紙に文字が浮かび上がって\nおみくじの結果が分かるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ when you do that‚ the letters will appear on the paper‚\nand you'll know the fortune slip result",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3333334000004,
          "startTime": 47.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.2999952953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。俺の結果は……おおっ、大吉だ！\n神様は怒っていなかったようだな、安心したよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. My result is… Oh‚ it's great blessing!\nIt seems the gods weren't angry‚ I'm relieved",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9900.000000000005,
          "startTime": 62.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3333273571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "不安が解けて良かったです\n次は私の番ですね。おみくじを濡らして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad your worries are over\nAnd it's my turn. soaking fortune slip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.3999940237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "文字が浮かび上がってきたが、これは……大凶！？\nおみくじで大凶なんて初めて見たぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The letters appeared‚ but this is… great misfortune!?\nIt's the first time I've seen great misfortune in a fortune slip",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.0666606904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは、{user}さんが参拝の方法を\n間違えた影響で、私も呪われてしまったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-This is because {user}-san got the pray order\nwrong‚ and I getting cursed too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0999940237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "この神社は縁結びでも有名だから……\nもしも縁結びの神様に祟られたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This shrine is famous for matchmaking…\nIf I'm suffered by the god of matchmaking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなや\n{user}さんとの縁を切られるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might lose all ties with\nHoshimi Prods. and {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6333273571
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなの嫌です！\n私、みんなと離れたくありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I don't like that!\nI don't want to be separated from everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 102.2999940237
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（大凶だったことが余程ショックだったようだ）\n（呪いを怖がる千紗をなんとか安心させたいが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It was a real shock that the great misfortune occurred）\n（I want to somehow reassure Chisa‚ who is afraid of curses…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……呪いがそんなに気になるなら\n俺と一緒にお祓いを受けてみるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…If you're so worried about the curse‚\nwould you like to receive a purification with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――お祓いを終えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the purification",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 118.1333353679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ありがとうございました\nお祓いしてもらって落ち着きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ thank you\nI feel much better now after the purification",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "祭壇の前で神主さんが私と{user}さんの\n名前を読み上げて……なんだか変な感じでしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The priest read out my name and {user}'s\nname in front of the altar… it felt a bit strange",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7171661173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7000001274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "まさか京都まで来て、千紗と一緒に\nお祓いを受けることになるとは想像もしてなかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never imagined I'd come all the way to Kyoto\nand receive an purification with Chisa",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "私もです。でも、いい経験になりました\nこれで呪いが消えてくれたらいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me‚ too. But‚ it was a good experience\nI hope this takes away the curse",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.5000001274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　もう一度おみくじを引いてみませんか？\n呪いが解けたのなら、運気も上がっているはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right! Would you like to drawing a fortune slip once more?\nIf the curse were gone‚ luck would have increased",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.1333334608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\n試しにやってみてもいいかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes sense…\nIt would be good to try it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3400.0000000000055,
